Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah pengangkatan menteri itu\Nsudah melebihi "pembinaan" semata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai pengganti... Putra Mahkota?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya masih belum tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu hanya bentuk kasih sayang,\Nmaka tidak masalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat. Sesuai perkataanmu, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dapat informasi\Ndari pejabat yang kusuap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam apel pagi besok,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia akan mengangkatku\Nsebagai Menteri Keuangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang Mulia terhadap Kanda Albert...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mari kita bersulang untuk perayaanmu\Ndan kecermatan analisismu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keats beserta 167 pasukannya\Ntelah kami tangkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berniat menggulingkan Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu setelah Yang Mulia purnabakti,\Nmereka akan mengangkat Putra Mahkota.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sudah mengakui rencana itu.\NSesuai informasi awal kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}50 tahun masa pemerintahan.\N35 tahun sebagai Putra Mahkota.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kesabarannya sudah habis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harap waspada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tak ada bukti Putra Mahkota\Nterlibat hal ini secara langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takkan menghukum Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eksekusi Keats dan pasukannya. Sekian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan Oscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi saya sudah mengutus\Npejabat yang dekat dengan Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya beliau sudah paham situasinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena di tempat itu\Njuga ada Pangeran Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti yang menyadari\Nmaksudku adalah Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdasarkan laporan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai harapanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah hebat seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gilbert tidak layak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu pun Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lantas siapa yang layak\Nmeneruskan takhtaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Henry? Oscar? Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa saja boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama dia berhasil menaklukkan\Nsecara gemilang ujian dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekian nama-nama pelaku\Nkasus makar kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan mereka semua\Nada di sekitar Kanda Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tangan kanan Kanda...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mantan pendidiknya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kesatria.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dari sudut pandang siapa pun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}jelas ini susunan orang\Ndari faksi putra mahkota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana tindakan Pangeran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pertanyaan yang wajar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Karena Kandaku diduga\Nterlibat dalam hal ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Menurut hukum Kekaisaran,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}meski anggota Kekaisaran melakukannya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}selalu ada pasal yang bisa\Nmeringankan hukumannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pengecualiannya hanya satu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yaitu makar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apabila anggota Kekaisaran\Nterlibat makar,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}baik sebagai pelaku utama maupun\Npembantu, hukumannya dipenggal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sekalipun hanya tahu tanda-tanda makar,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tapi tidak melaporkan pada Kaisar,\Nkesalahannya tetap sama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan jajaran orang\Nyang punya hubungan erat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}mustahil Kanda tak tahu apa pun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Namun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}makar oleh Putra Mahkota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Lalu hukuman mati.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu akan menjadi skandal luar biasa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang bahkan dapat\Nmengguncang Kekaisaran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada titah dari Yang Mulia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Bacakan kembali\Nputusan seperti yang tertulis."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka harus dijatuhi hukuman setimpal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham kehendak Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hukuman akan diumumkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada perlu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perihal makar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penetapan hukuman telah diputuskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putusan berlaku hanya\Nbagi mereka yang tertangkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelaku utama dijatuhi hukuman pancung.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembantu dan komplotan\Ndijatuhi hukuman mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya dilaksanakan\Nhari ini juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalau dibatasi pada "mereka" saja,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}berarti dalam tingkat ini, Yang Mulia\Nbelum ingin menyeret Kanda Albert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Maka, hukumannya hanya\Nuntuk yang tercantum di daftar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Waktu hukuman mati pun harusnya bisa\Nditunda sampai eksekusi massal tahunan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Namun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}kalau amnesti dapat memicu dugaan\Npublik bahwa Kanda terlibat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}maka pilihannya adalah\Npelaksanaan segera.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sehingga semuanya masih\Ndalam ranah hukum Kekaisaran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah sudah melaksanakan tugasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tambahkan seribu riin\Npada tunjangan tahunannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini bukan sesuatu\Nyang pantas diberi imbalan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ternyata memang beliau\Ntidak ingin melibatkan Kanda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memang hebat, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan terus mengharapkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bekerjalah lebih baik lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kau kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyusupnya... masih ada di dalam...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil bala bantuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergilah ke Kementerian Pertahanan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tunggu, momen ini...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumpulkan seluruh sekutu kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak boleh ada yang keluar selainku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai ada yang masuk,\Nsekalipun dia Pangeran!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pa-Pangeran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua pejabat sipil, mundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lembek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takkan kubiarkan bunuh diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kita mundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga. Semua sudah Anda kalahkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana situasinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Korban di pihak penjaga\Nseperti yang Anda lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, para pelaku makar,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semuanya sudah dibunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pembungkaman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Artinya, orang-orang ini adalah suruhan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kanda Albert, Sang Putra Mahkota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang Anda lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dilukai mereka berempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika pangeran mengalami luka berat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa hukuman terberat bagi pelakunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hukuman mati,\Ndilaksanakan saat itu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka, segera lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eksekusi telah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begini,\Nmasalah ini sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Astaga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sekali saja salah langkah, negeri ini\Nakan terguncang. Dasar Putra Mahkota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya izin menghadap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena sudah memanggilmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kondisimu perlu diperhatikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak usah terlalu formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas pertimbangannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atas kegagalan kali ini, sebenarnya\Nsaya malu untuk menghadap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan tanggung jawabmu seorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai bisa melukai pria sekuatmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa berarti mereka\Nmemang setangguh itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sudah kuduga akan seperti ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini ulah jaringan informasi Yang Mulia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mereka pasti tahu kalau aku\Nyang mengoyak diriku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal kekuatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya kira ini bukan hanya\Ntentang kemampuan berpedang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sehebat apa pun seseorang,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bila diincar kelemahan mentalnya,\Npasti akan sedikit goyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memiliki putra cakap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepatnya, aku dianugerahi putra hebat\Nyang takkan mempermalukan namaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sepertinya beliau telah paham\Nbahwa tindakanku ini kuambil{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}setelah melalui banyak pertimbangan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai yang lain sepertimu,\Naku juga akan terbantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa berjalan-jalan sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau tahu, Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaisar yang kelak dikenang\Nsebagai penguasa bijak,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sembilan dari sepuluh orang\Nakan menodai akhir hayatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa ini membahas\Nmakar Putra Mahkota?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kaisar sudah menuntun negeri ini\Nmenuju masa keemasan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pasti beliau akan dicatat sebagai\Npenguasa bijak di kitab sejarah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Namun, andai makarnya berhasil,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tentu akan tertulis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}bahwa dia pikun di akhir hayat, sampai\Ntak mampu mengendalikan putranya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Beliau memang sudah\Ntak percaya lagi pada Putra Mahkota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Alasannya masih belum bertindak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}karena menurunkan Putra Mahkota\Ndari kedudukannya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}akan menodai akhir hayatnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan penuh hormat,\Nsaya ingin memohon suatu hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kanda Henry, Kanda Oscar,\Ndan juga saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walau kami sudah diangkat\Nsebagai menteri kekaisaran,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena ini pengalaman pertama kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin saja nantinya\Nkami akan khilaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka dari itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami akan bersyukur jika ada sosok\Nyang menyatukan dan mengarahkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau meminta Kanselir Utama diutus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ini hanya perandaian, ada\Nkedudukan yang "mengatur segalanya".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang berada di atas kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya mengajukan usulan agar dibentuk\N"Menteri Agung Keluarga Kekaisaran."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, kedudukan itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya ingin Putra Mahkota\Nyang menjabatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu akan menyentuh luka lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pulang saja hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjadi putra mahkota selama 35 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga paham perasaan\NKanda yang sudah lama menanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan menyerahkan keputusan akhir\Npada Yang Mulia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}biarkan Kanda menjalankan\Nperan seperti Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia akan berada\Ndi atas para menteri, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika masalah\Npenting ditolak Menteri Agung,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tak menyampaikannya padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk mencegah hal itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kiranya setiap Menteri Keluarga Kekaisaran\Ndiberikan hak pengaduan langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika setiap menteri\Nmenilai masalah itu krusial,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka masalah itu dapat disampaikan\Nlangsung pada Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan begini, Putra Mahkota\Ntak memegang kekuasaan sepenuhnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}"Menteri Agung Keluarga Kekaisaran,"\Nadalah kedudukan yang tak berpengaruh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kedudukan tanpa kuasa sejati.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau memang bisa menyelesaikan,\Nmaka itu jalan terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah, terima kasih usulanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Usulan itu akan kuterima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya merasa sangat terhormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai saja kau\Nsudah terlahir lebih awal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Beliau memahami langsung saranku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Beliau memang pantas dijuluki\Npenguasa bijak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan tidak menodai akhir hayatnya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}maka itu jalan terbaik\Nagar semua rakyat hidup tenteram.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus memberimu hadiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Usulan sebagus ini\Ntak sepadan dengan uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cruz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Antar kami ke gedung pusaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cincin itu dahulu ditemukan\Nberkat kejelian matamu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melihat kejelianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pilihlah satu benda\Nsesuai yang kau suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas tawarannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Carilah, Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mimpi singkat yang masih tak sampai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kutakut akan peluh\NYang tak kunjung sembuh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Siluet terpantul di tepi jendela{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kenanganku bersamamu\Nperlahan memudar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Diterangi sinar rembulan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kulihat dirimu bersinar\NBagai bintang nun jauh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:23:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Walau musim berganti, waktu berlalu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rasaku padamu tidak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Harapku agar sajak cinta abadi ini\NKian sampai padamu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Walau kutahu kan terwujud\NAku tetap memimpikannya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Air mataku mengering{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an3}Pemandangan mengabur\NDi seberang keabadian{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an3}Walau aku terlepas bayang-bayangmu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Hatiku kan terpaut di sisimu{\i0}
